text: Oğuz Ceylan (born 15 December 1990) is a Turkish footballer who plays as a rightback for Gaziantep F.K.. ==Professional career== Ceylan made his professional debut with Gazişehir Gaziantep in a 4-1 Süper Lig win over Gençlerbirliği S.K. on 26 August 2019. ==References== ==External links== * * * Mackolik Profile Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:People from Çanakkale Category:Turkish footballers Category:Gaziantep F.K. footballers Category:Kartalspor footballers Category:Beşiktaş J.K. footballers Category:Çaykur Rizespor footballers Category:Siirtspor footballers Category:Süper Lig players Category:TFF First League players Category:Association football fullbacks
